"Legal, Rules, Parameters; Preview moved to a side panel. Changelog tab added."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:89
